{"tid":1826282,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【阿嫲級女優】81歲處女下海 小笠原祐子只吃嫩男","createTime":"2020-01-16T04:06:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-16T10:34:50.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8a1702d3217ac59019bb6fe5406d76de70f4336a","tid":1826282,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T04:06:20.000Z","msg":"在日本AV業界中，每年均有不少女生爭住獻身，當中包括現年84歲的「阿嫲級女優」小笠原祐子，三年前出道的她直言只會吃年輕小鮮肉，謝絕其他同輩熟男。<br />\n<br />\n據《AERA.dot》網站報道，小笠原祐子的父母都很嚴格，她在大學畢業後，在工作時才認識初戀男友。兩人結婚後，她為丈夫誕下兩男一女。小笠原祐子的丈夫於59歲時因病離世，她在母親和妹妹的鼓勵下才能重新振作，到處旅遊玩樂，之後更結識到大學生男友，但兩人並沒有發生肉體關係。當時經營小餐館的小笠原祐子，被女顧客問到會否有興趣拍AV，還邀請她到AV拍攝現場參觀，當時小笠原祐子看到年輕女優與熟男做愛，便說着：「如果是我的話，就不會跟老伯做愛，不是年輕帥哥的話很討厭。」AV製作人聽到小笠原祐子的話後，隨即表示會為她準備鮮肉，而她最後亦爽快答應演出。當時已81歲高齡的小笠原祐子，除了丈夫之外，沒有跟其他男人發生過性行為，她又指兒子知道她下海拍AV，還鼓勵她做自己喜歡做的事。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200115/large/1579085760_5365.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200115%2Flarge%2F1579085760_5365.jpg&h=434b7bdb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200115/large/1579085771_5853.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200115%2Flarge%2F1579085771_5853.jpg&h=04d08d9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200116/WL4W2SEMU3PWUXJZ4UX3OXXOB4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200116%2FWL4W2SEMU3PWUXJZ4UX3OXXOB4%2F&d=LzGu2J%2BtBqWvyoHzd7Q7GMTiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=5104f3df\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200116%2FWL4W2SEMU3PWUXJZ4UX3OXXOB4%2F&h=9c82bc08\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200116/WL4W2SEMU3PWUXJZ4UX3OXXOB4/</a>"},{"pid":"2ea8337539c9538f70c8edc696416afb3a309b4c","tid":1826282,"uid":35106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T04:11:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"120bf6c14e3587e9a1ae3f3c503874fcef851cae","tid":1826282,"uid":96406,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T04:12:10.000Z","msg":"薑檸樂"},{"pid":"3f43f2b92e01197c4b931c5f8d9989c666062874","tid":1826282,"uid":22560,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T04:13:08.000Z","msg":"後生成個irene 咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a120c93b5300cf2098f57be340dff6d30642e39","tid":1826282,"uid":80516,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T04:14:06.000Z","msg":"佢果個年代有讀大學，仲要係女性，其實本身應該好屈機下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78718a84bcc9cea43ac24e31c73243950eed0eca","tid":1826282,"uid":165749,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T04:23:24.000Z","msg":"開放既社會係81碎既大媽都可以享受魚水之歡"},{"pid":"11c4d74cb66b48753f8952884dafe76c5a00fc89","tid":1826282,"uid":34071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f43f2b92e01197c4b931c5f8d9989c666062874","tid":1826282,"uid":22560,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T04:13:08.000Z","msg":"後生成個irene 咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T04:26:44.000Z","msg":"Irene=老女人 fced"},{"pid":"c19b963bc50a8696a5e8ba13b22d526d57d1836e","tid":1826282,"uid":149371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11c4d74cb6